{"tid":681563,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"話說頭先去泳池游水","createTime":"2018-05-28T07:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T08:32:59.000Z","uid":162644,"like":155,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a0fcd46fc61a535c7925ada54a9d6242d31e6494","tid":681563,"uid":162644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T07:04:46.000Z","msg":"游到咁上下諗住去曬下太陽<br />\n點知d沙灘椅10張有6張有人<br />\n淨低4張有d毛巾呀太陽油就咁放係到霸位<br />\n咁我就去求其一張拎走d太陽油放係張椅則邊<br />\n就上去曬左15分鐘到<br />\n忽然有個睇落30歲左右既男人行埋黎<br />\n<br />\n男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 哥仔唔好意思張椅我用緊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下？我見無人我先用架喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁你見唔到上面有支太陽油係到咩？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我指撚住則邊個牌（請勿以物品霸佔沙灘椅）你睇下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> .....<br />\n<br />\n之後見到個男人個樣on99咁走左去<br />\n<br />\n成日話d蝗好無公德心實情香港人又咪一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主好波<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 還番張椅比人啦"},{"pid":"ab0e2df9439a376e6a70f53cc6973499bc18f734","tid":681563,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T07:06:29.000Z","msg":"又夠鐘幫支那洗底"},{"pid":"253799c5a0c8ff4f43a488f6006a841714d581aa","tid":681563,"uid":162644,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"ab0e2df9439a376e6a70f53cc6973499bc18f734","tid":681563,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T07:06:29.000Z","msg":"又夠鐘幫支那洗底"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T07:10:00.000Z","msg":"蝗同香港人都係半斤八兩<br />\n洗咩底？"},{"pid":"c466c59e79d2aadba76645da65db92b77b67b5f0","tid":681563,"uid":25560